These are instructions for creating a release of the Teyjus system.
These are to be executed from the root of the Teyjus directory.

 1. Edit 'source/front/parseargs.ml' and 'dune-project' to set the version number
 2. Execute 'make test' and confirm that all tests are passing
    ('dune runtest' will catch tests known to fail)
 3. Set a tag to the version number 'git tag vX.X.X' to create a tarball